  <name>Context Studio</name>
  <summary>AI-friendly project context aggregation tool</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Context Studio is a desktop application for assembling AI-friendly project context. 
      It scans a local codebase, lets you selectively pick files, and outputs a well-formatted 
      context document ready to paste into any LLM conversation.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Smart Ignore Engine matching .gitignore and framework presets</li>
      <li>Privacy Filter to mask API keys and secrets</li>
      <li>Drag-and-drop context organization for LLM attention</li>
      <li>Live token counting powered by Tiktoken</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

